channel.title: How to Portforward With Telenet Router
channel.description:
[size=14pt]MY FIRST TURT PLEASE BE NICE[/size]
Welcome Belgium Users, Its really easy just read good and look good to the pics :) Good Luck :)
First and all you need to go to https://www.telenet.be/mijntelenet/
Login with ur Telenet Username and password [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/1erho6.jpg[/img]
When you logged in you will get this page Click on Mijn Internet (My Internet) [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/ih87t1.jpg[/img]
Scroll Down Till You Se Geavanceerd Click on Geavanceerd Than Click On Portforwarding [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/eain1c.jpg[/img]
Now open CMD When it opened write in it IPCONFIG Use This last 3numbers of your IP ADRESS for portforwarding [color=black](hese are my numbers these numbers will not work for you)[/color] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/ohiplu.jpg[/img]
Okay Now Put These 3Numbers here @ Begin poort Eind poort (start port and end port) write your server PORT NOT IP Protocol pick BEIDE (BOTH) Status pick Actief (ONLINE)
Pic: [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/k3azw4.jpg[/img]
So here you go you portforwarded you own server! Contrags!!!
[size=12pt]DONT FORGOT TO SAVE IT![/size]
~~~~~~~~Credits~~~~~~~~ DingDongDing Telenet
Sorry For My English Found any bad english word please comment it and tell me :P
